query:
SELECT p.id, p.title, p.slug as page_slug, m.slug as module_slug, d.slug as discipline_slug 
FROM pages p 
JOIN modules m ON p.moduleId = m.id 
JOIN disciplines d ON m.disciplineId = d.id 
ORDER BY p.id 
LIMIT 10;
